text: Læa meux di mi khamphir chbab hnung cak thi xallxhˌ mayang phwk khea sung yunyan nı sing thi mi xyu kab phwk khea thang «thi phwk khea khey khx hı mi chaychna henux br rda phu thi ptiseth sraththa ma kxn khran meux sing thi phwk khea rucak di di mayang phwk khea læw phwk khea klab ptiseth sing nan seiy dangnan khwam hang kil cak reaa hˌmat khx ngxallxhˌ cung tk xyu kæ brrda phu ptiseth hela nan
